      <title>特朗普在枪击事件后首次向共和党发表讲话：值得关注的话题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/trump-speech-at-rnc-2024-is-first-after-shooting-what-to-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普将于周四晚间发表自正式成为总统候选人并躲过暗杀以来的首次共和党演讲，他的演讲旨在团结共和党人击败总统乔·拜登。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/trump-speech-at-rnc-2024-is-first-after-shooting-what-to-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
