    <item>
      <title>拜登最新减免 12 亿美元学生贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-forgives-1-2-billion-in-student-loans-in-latest-relief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登周四取消了公务员额外的 12 亿美元学生债务，这是他在连任竞选期间提供贷款减免和兑现其标志性举措之一的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-forgives-1-2-billion-in-student-loans-in-latest-relief</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚考虑对银行外汇利润征收一次性 50% 暴利税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/nigeria-mulls-one-time-50-windfall-tax-on-bank-forex-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布计划对银行在去年奈拉贬值后因巨额货币收益而获得的暴利征收 50% 的一次性税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/nigeria-mulls-one-time-50-windfall-tax-on-bank-forex-profits</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:56:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国誓言推动高质量发展作为“首要任务”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/china-vows-to-push-for-high-quality-development-as-top-mission</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家主席习近平承诺要让高质量发展成为世界第二大经济体的指导力量，并制定了推动中国在应对国内经济放缓和中美贸易紧张局势的同时向前发展的长期愿景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/china-vows-to-push-for-high-quality-development-as-top-mission</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:35:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告发现欧盟凝聚基金需要进行根本性改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/eu-cohesion-funds-need-a-fundamental-revamp-report-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲经济研究中心的报告显示，欧盟用来消除 27 个成员国中较贫穷和较富裕地区之间差异的 3920 亿欧元工具需要进行彻底改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/eu-cohesion-funds-need-a-fundamental-revamp-report-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:13:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
