      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/kenya-police-warn-anti-ruto-protesters-to-stay-out-of-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚警方以安全威胁为由警告反政府抗议者不要进入首都内罗毕。]]></description>
